This is a minimal implimentation of the kids tool logo.
I have tried to draw some fuctle figures using this minimal functions.

turtle.py    -----> a simple python class to create turtle graphics.
anti_koch.py -----> a simple python code to draw  anti_koch curve.
snowflake.py -----> a simple python code to draw  koch snowflake.
snowflake_quadratic_type_1.py----> a simple python code to draw koch snowflake quadratic curve (90) type1
snowflake_quadratic_type_2.py----> a simple python code to draw koch snowflake quadratic cureve type2. 
